&lt;p&gt;LAHORE: A sessions court on Tuesday ordered singer Meesha Shafi to pay singer-cum-actor Ali Zafar Rs5 million in damages.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The court issued a short order in a defamation case filed against Shafi by Zafar for levelling allegations of sexual harassment.&lt;/p&gt;
